---
import { heroStats, profile } from '../../../data/portfolio';
---

<section id="inicio" class="grid items-center gap-7 py-5 sm:py-6 lg:grid-cols-[1.2fr_0.8fr] lg:py-10">
	<div class="rounded-4xl border border-ink/8 bg-surface/88 p-4 shadow-sm shadow-black/5 sm:p-6 lg:p-7">
		<p class="mb-4 inline-flex rounded-full border border-gold-main/30 bg-gold-main/10 px-3.5 py-1.5 text-[0.68rem] font-medium uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-violet-deep sm:px-4 sm:py-2 sm:text-xs sm:tracking-[0.28em]">
			{profile.name}
		</p>
		<h1 class="max-w-3xl font-serif text-[clamp(2rem,9vw,4.4rem)] leading-none text-ink lg:text-7xl">
			{profile.role}
		</h1>
		<p class="mt-5 max-w-2xl text-base leading-7 text-ink/72 sm:mt-6 sm:text-xl sm:leading-8">
			{profile.intro}
		</p>
		<p class="mt-3.5 max-w-2xl text-[0.95rem] leading-6 text-ink/62 sm:mt-4 sm:text-lg sm:leading-7">
			Si necesitas una web que proyecte mejor tu negocio, ordene tu presencia digital y te ayude a generar más confianza, puedo ayudarte a construirla.
		</p>

		<div class="mt-5 flex flex-wrap gap-2.5 sm:mt-6 sm:gap-3">
			<span class="rounded-full border border-violet-main/18 bg-violet-soft/35 px-3 py-1.5 text-[0.68rem] font-medium uppercase tracking-[0.14em] text-violet-deep sm:text-xs sm:tracking-[0.2em]">
				Diseño + desarrollo
			</span>
			<span class="rounded-full border border-gold-main/20 bg-gold-main/10 px-3 py-1.5 text-[0.68rem] font-medium uppercase tracking-[0.14em] text-violet-deep sm:text-xs sm:tracking-[0.2em]">
				Enfoque en conversión
			</span>
			<span class="rounded-full border border-ink/10 bg-paper/80 px-3 py-1.5 text-[0.68rem] font-medium uppercase tracking-[0.14em] text-ink/65 sm:text-xs sm:tracking-[0.2em]">
				Entrega clara
			</span>
		</div>

		<div class="mt-7 grid gap-3 sm:mt-8 sm:grid-cols-2 xl:grid-cols-3">
			{heroStats.map((stat) => (
				<div class="rounded-3xl border border-ink/8 bg-paper/82 p-4 shadow-sm shadow-black/5 sm:p-5">
					<p class="text-2xl font-bold text-gold-main sm:text-3xl">{stat.value}</p>
					<p class="mt-2 text-sm text-ink/62">{stat.label}</p>
				</div>
			))}
		</div>

		<div class="mt-7 grid gap-3 sm:mt-8 sm:flex sm:flex-wrap sm:gap-4">
			<button
				type="button"
				data-open-section="proyectos"
				class="inline-flex justify-center rounded-full bg-gold-main px-5 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-ink transition hover:bg-gold-soft sm:px-6 sm:text-base"
			>
				Ver trabajos
			</button>
			<button
				type="button"
				data-open-section="contacto"
				class="inline-flex justify-center rounded-full border border-ink/10 bg-surface px-5 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-ink transition hover:border-gold-main/40 hover:bg-paper sm:px-6 sm:text-base"
			>
				Pedir presupuesto
			</button>
		</div>
	</div>

	<div class="relative">
		<div class="absolute inset-0 rotate-6 rounded-4xl bg-linear-to-br from-gold-main/26 via-transparent to-violet-soft/24 blur-sm sm:blur-md"></div>
		<div class="relative overflow-hidden rounded-4xl border border-ink/8 bg-surface/88 p-4 shadow-lg shadow-black/8 sm:p-5 sm:shadow-xl sm:backdrop-blur-xl lg:p-6">
			<div class="flex flex-wrap items-center justify-between gap-2 border-b border-ink/8 pb-4 sm:gap-3 sm:pb-5">
				<div>
					<p class="text-[0.72rem] uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-gold-soft sm:text-sm sm:tracking-[0.24em]">Perfil</p>
					<h2 class="mt-2 font-serif text-2xl text-ink sm:text-3xl">Presencia digital con estilo</h2>
				</div>
				<div class="rounded-full border border-gold-main/35 bg-gold-main/12 px-3 py-1 text-xs text-violet-deep sm:text-sm">
					Disponible
				</div>
			</div>

			<div class="mt-5 space-y-4 sm:mt-6">
				<div class="rounded-3xl bg-violet-soft/35 p-4 sm:p-5">
					<p class="text-[0.72rem] uppercase tracking-[0.16em] text-violet-soft sm:text-sm sm:tracking-[0.2em]">Enfoque</p>
					<p class="mt-2 text-base text-ink sm:text-lg">Diseño y desarrollo orientados a mejorar imagen, claridad de oferta y capacidad de conversión.</p>
				</div>
				<div class="grid gap-4 sm:grid-cols-2">
					<div class="rounded-3xl border border-ink/8 bg-paper/80 p-4 sm:p-5">
						<p class="text-sm text-ink/55">Especialidad</p>
						<p class="mt-2 font-semibold text-ink">Landings, webs corporativas, frontend visual y aplicaciones MVC</p>
					</div>
					<div class="rounded-3xl border border-ink/8 bg-paper/80 p-4 sm:p-5">
						<p class="text-sm text-ink/55">Estilo visual</p>
						<p class="mt-2 font-semibold text-ink">Estética actual, contraste fuerte y lectura clara en móvil y desktop</p>
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="rounded-3xl border border-gold-main/20 bg-gold-main/10 p-4">
					<p class="text-[0.72rem] uppercase tracking-[0.16em] text-violet-deep sm:text-sm">Objetivo de cada proyecto</p>
					<p class="mt-2 text-sm leading-6 text-ink/75 sm:text-base">
						Que tu web se vea bien, se entienda rápido y convierta mejor en consultas o ventas.
					</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</section>